21:15.000 --> 21:18.000
Like everything else, if we want to work safe,

21:18.000 --> 21:21.000
we have to think and we have to plan.

21:23.000 --> 21:27.000
The best thing we can do is to avoid manual handling entirely.

21:27.000 --> 21:29.000
Take an example.

21:29.000 --> 21:31.000
We have to erect frames.

21:31.000 --> 21:34.000
Think about mechanization and using handling aids.

21:34.000 --> 21:36.000
For example, we could use a crane.

21:36.000 --> 21:38.000
It may seem obvious,

21:38.000 --> 21:40.000
but that is the best way to eliminate

21:40.000 --> 21:42.000
the risk of manual handling injuries.

21:42.000 --> 21:44.000
Use machines.

