large vertical movement,

22:02.000 --> 22:04.000
long carrying distances,

22:04.000 --> 22:06.000
generous pushing or pulling,

22:06.000 --> 22:08.000
repetitive handling,

22:08.000 --> 22:10.000
insufficient rest or recovery time,

22:10.000 --> 22:13.000
a work rate imposed by a process.

22:14.000 --> 22:16.000
We might have assessed

22:16.000 --> 22:19.000
