22:19.000 --> 22:23.000
So, what can we do to control the risk?

22:23.000 --> 22:27.000
How can you make the work safer and easier?

22:29.000 --> 22:33.000
You can make the load lighter or less bulky,

22:33.000 --> 22:36.000
easier to grasp, more stable,

22:36.000 --> 22:39.000
less damaging to hold.

22:44.000 --> 22:48.000
We are all at risk of manual handling injuries.

